      "prompt": "Invoke axon4to5-migrate at $SKILL_DIR with `framework=axon configuration=spring mode=single source=$SOURCE`. LoggingCommandHandlerInterceptor implements MessageHandlerInterceptor<CommandMessage<?>> with AF4 `Object handle(UnitOfWork<? extends CommandMessage<?>> unitOfWork, InterceptorChain interceptorChain) throws Exception`. Body uses: `unitOfWork.getMessage()`, `unitOfWork.onCommit(uow -> {...})`, `unitOfWork.onRollback(uow -> {...})`, returns `interceptorChain.proceed()`. Apply the interceptors recipe (use-case 02): rewrite to `MessageStream<?> interceptOnHandle(CommandMessage message, ProcessingContext context, MessageHandlerInterceptorChain<CommandMessage> chain)` — use `message` param directly (drop `unitOfWork.getMessage()`); `unitOfWork.onCommit(...)` → `context.runOnAfterCommit(ctx -> {...})`; `unitOfWork.onRollback(...)` → `context.onError((ctx, error) -> {...})`; `return interceptorChain.proceed()` → `return chain.proceed(message, context)`. Remove `throws Exception`. Generic: `CommandMessage<?>` → `CommandMessage`. Remove AF4 imports: `org.axonframework.commandhandling.CommandMessage`, `org.axonframework.messaging.InterceptorChain`, `org.axonframework.messaging.MessageHandlerInterceptor`, `org.axonframework.messaging.unitofwork.UnitOfWork`. Add AF5 imports: `org.axonframework.messaging.commandhandling.CommandMessage`, `org.axonframework.messaging.core.MessageHandlerInterceptor`, `org.axonframework.messaging.core.MessageHandlerInterceptorChain`, `org.axonframework.messaging.core.MessageStream`, `org.axonframework.messaging.core.unitofwork.ProcessingContext`. @Component preserved. Copy the Result block to $WORKSPACE/result.md.",
